Plains Dwarves are the lowest of the low among the dwarves of Curionr. Living primarily on the surface, they are often shunned by other dwarves, however they are more accustomed to interacting with other races, as well as hard manual labor. Nevertheless, they are typically poor and ill-educated. Their life on the open plain has endowed them with a dark tan tone to their skin (particularly compared to the pale deep dwarves).
