Half-Dwarves
The rare offspring of a dwarf and a human, Half-Dwarves look like thick, powerful somewhat shorter than average humans or very tall, somewhat gangly dwarves. While they are almost unheard of in most lands, there is a small but vibrant community of half-dwarves in the border region between Curinor and Gerasalim. Half-Dwarves are not so insular as other dwarves, but they tend to be ponderous and slow to react
